name: Abstract Generative/EagleView (RARE EDITION)
description:
In this collection, with an abstract look at urban life, I show the passage and bustle of urban dwellers.
The movement of cars, buildings, and flashing lights in the urban landscape are the elements that I try to portray in an exaggerated and minimalist way, the "EAGLE VIEW " is the name of this collection.
Generative artwork exploring color and the emergent effect of stacking simple shapes and filling their intersections.which take you on the journey to an imaginary universe. All artworks are created using custom algorithms in processing.
